  "texts": [
    "The enriched query formulation and the ranking process, encapsulated in the mathematical representation, reveal the complexity and efficacy of the retrieval mechanism.",
    "Experiments and Results Experimental SetupThe experimental environment comprised a high-performance computing cluster equipped with NVIDIA A100 GPUs, each possessing 80GB of memory, and interconnected via a highspeed InfiniBand network.",
    "The Llama model, augmented with the reverse proxy-style Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG) mechanism, was deployed and evaluated within this environment.",
    "The experimental setup also included several external data sources, such as structured databases, knowledge graphs, and unstructured text corpora, to provide a comprehensive retrieval base for the RAG system.The evaluation metrics employed in the experiments were designed to measure both the factual accuracy and the coherence of the generated responses.",
    "Precision, recall, and F1-score were utilized to quantify the accuracy of the responses, while BLEU (Bilingual Evaluation Understudy) and ROUGE (Recall-Oriented Understudy for Gisting Evaluation) scores were used to assess the coherence and relevance of the generated text."
